PN,40101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FA gang who used drones to smuggle
OL,8,Fdrugs, weapons, and phones into
OL,9,FBritain's prisons in a system likened
OL,10,Fto Deliveroo and Uber Eats for inmates
OL,11,Fhave been jailed.
OL,13,FShafaghatullah Mohseni, 29,
OL,14,Forchestrated dozens of late night and
OL,15,Fearly morning "drops" at prisons
OL,16,Facross London and the South East of
OL,17,FEngland between December 2 2024 and
OL,18,FFebruary 26 2025.
OL,26,@wD@OOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
