OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FHashim Al-Hussaini, 28, Mohammed
OL,8,FHamoud, 22, Faiz Salah, 29, Zahar
OL,9,FEssaghi, 51, Mustafa Ibrahim, 30, and
OL,10,FEmanuel Fisniku, 25, assisted Mohseni,
OL,11,Facting as lookouts and drivers, as
OL,12,Fwell as receiving payments for the
OL,13,Fillicit shipments.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FHarrow Crown Court, sitting at Hendon
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court, heard at least two
OL,9,Fflick knives were among contraband
OL,10,Fplanned to be smuggled into the
OL,11,Fprisons, as well as packages of drugs
OL,12,Fincluding cannabis, Xanax and Valium,
OL,13,Fand tiny mobile phones that could be
OL,14,Fhidden from guards.
OL,16,FJudge James Lofthouse said it was a
OL,17,F"well-oiled conspiracy" which prison
OL,18,Fguards struggled to tackle ` even if
OL,19,Fthey had actually seen the drones
OL,20,Fmaking the drop-offs at cell windows.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FStaff shortages meant guards could
OL,8,Fhead to the cells to watch ` through
OL,9,Fthe door hatch ` as "prisoners were
OL,10,Fstuffing items behind pipes".
OL,12,FBut by the time enough prison staff
OL,13,Fwere available to conduct a search,
OL,14,Fthe illicit items had vanished, said
OL,15,Fthe judge.
OL,26,@qD@UOUrD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,F"Those who conspire for profit to
OL,8,Fflood our prisons with drugs and
OL,9,Fmobile phones, and are heedless to
OL,10,Fwhatever else including weapons they
OL,11,Fsmuggle in, facilitate further
OL,12,Fcriminality, and undermine the general
OL,13,Frunning and good order of our
OL,14,Fprisons", said the judge.
OL,16,FHe said inmates had items delivered
OL,17,F"to order", and criticised the
OL,18,F"corrosive" impact on prison safety
OL,19,Fand security from drones arriving with
OL,20,Fpackages "as if by Uber Eats or
OL,21,FDeliveroo".
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@HO]yD@AOUyD@JO]zD@AOUzD@KO]|D@
OL,26,AJOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FMohseni, referred to in court as the
OL,8,F"grand delivery driver", was sentenced
OL,9,Fto five years and three months in
OL,10,Fprison as the leader of the
OL,11,Fconspiracy, having arranged drops in
OL,12,Fphone calls to prisoners and their
OL,13,Frelatives and received more than
OL,14,F#30,000 in payments for the drone
OL,15,Fflights.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FAl-Hussaini, Hamoud, and Essaghi were
OL,8,Fsentenced to 33 months in prison,
OL,9,FSalah was jailed for 31 months,
OL,10,FIbrahim received a sentence of 30
OL,11,Fmonths in prison, and Fisniku was
OL,12,Fjailed for 27 months.
OL,14,FThe Metropolitan Police said the gang
OL,15,Fwas responsible for 75% of all drone
OL,16,Fdrops into London prisons between
OL,17,FDecember 2024 and February 2025.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FAll seven defendants admitted their
OL,8,Froles in a "serious, organised, and
OL,9,Fprolific enterprise" to supply Class B
OL,10,Fand C drugs, and conveying list A and
OL,11,FB articles into prisons.
OL,13,FThey would travel by car to the
OL,14,Fprisons, often in the early hours of
OL,15,Fthe morning, and fly packages filled
OL,16,Fwith contraband through cell windows.
OL,26,@pD@LOUqD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FThe gang targeted at least nine
OL,8,Fprisons including Wormwood Scrubs,
OL,9,FBrixton, Pentonville, Wandsworth,
OL,10,FNorwich, and Leicester, the court
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FOpening the case on Monday, prosecutor
OL,8,FSam Barker said: "Operation Buzzbin
OL,9,Fwas a major police investigation
OL,10,Fconducted by the Metropolitan Police's
OL,11,FSpecialist Crime Command to
OL,12,Finvestigate drones being used to
OL,13,Fconvey drugs, mobile telephones, USB
OL,14,Fsticks, and other contraband into
OL,15,Fprisons across the South East of
OL,16,FEngland.
OL,26,@pD@ROU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,F"In total there were 70 different
OL,8,Fvisits by the conspiracy group to
OL,9,Fprisons between December 2 2024 and
OL,10,FFebruary 26 2025, so the conspiracy
OL,11,Fran until the involvement of the
OL,12,Fpolice for a period of 86 days."
OL,14,FThe court heard police arrested
OL,15,FMohseni, Al-Hussaini, Hamoud, and
OL,16,FFisniku travelling by car to a drop at
OL,17,FHMP Norwich on February 26 last year
OL,18,Fafter being tipped off that a knife
OL,19,Fwas going to be smuggled into the
OL,20,Fprison.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FThey found a JD sports bag in the car
OL,8,Fwith a drone, two packages containing
OL,9,Fphones and cannabis, and a knife.
OL,11,FThe prosecution has accepted that the
OL,12,Fconspirators "may not have been aware"
OL,13,Fthat in one of the flights they
OL,14,Fconveyed a flick knife in one of the
OL,15,Fpackages.
OL,17,F"But the fact is they did convey one
OL,18,Fof the knives," added Mr Barker.
OL,26,@tD@NOUtD@fO]yD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FThe conspirators were initially
OL,8,Fcharged with conspiring to convey a
OL,9,Fknife into a prison, which has since
OL,10,Fbeen dropped as the defendants may not
OL,11,Fhave packed the packages themselves.
OL,13,FMost of the 70 operations saw more
OL,14,Fthan one flight take place, and the
OL,15,Fconspirators have been estimated to
OL,16,Fhave made roughly 140 flights in total.
OL,18,FAlong with cannabis, the conspirators
OL,19,Falso smuggled Xanax and Valium and
OL,20,Fwere initially accused of smuggling
OL,21,Fcocaine, but this was later dropped.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FOne of the drones was recovered by
OL,8,Fpolice after it crashed into a woman's
OL,9,Fbackyard near HMP Wandsworth, the
OL,10,Fcourt heard.
OL,12,FShe told officers that a man had
OL,13,Fknocked on her door to collect the
OL,14,Fdrone in the early hours of the
OL,15,Fmorning, but she had refused his entry.
OL,17,FClose relatives of prisoners were
OL,18,Ffound to have sent large sums of money
OL,19,Fto Mohseni, as payment for the items,
OL,20,Fthe court heard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,F"The headline is that Mr Mohseni
OL,8,Freceived #26,785 from 14 individuals
OL,9,Fwho are directly linked to a serving
OL,10,Fprisoner, at a prison where he was
OL,11,Fdelivering items," said Mr Barker.
OL,13,FMohseni was at the centre of a "web of
OL,14,Ffinancial transfers" which saw him
OL,15,Freceive money and then pay the rest of
OL,16,Fhis co-conspirators.
OL,18,FDefending him, Michael McAlinden, said
OL,19,Fthat Mohseni began the offending as a
OL,20,Fmeans to pay off his debts.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@RO]uD@`OUvD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FMohseni, of Edgware, Salah, of north-
OL,8,Fwest London, Essaghi, of north-west
OL,9,FLondon, Ibrahim of Harrow Weald,
OL,10,FFisniku of Islington, Al-Hussaini, of
OL,11,FHarrow, and Hamoud, also of Harrow
OL,12,Fwere all told they must serve 40% of
OL,13,Ftheir sentences before being released
OL,14,Fon licence.
OL,16,FConcluding the sentencing hearing,
OL,17,FJudge Lofthouse commended the work of
OL,18,FMet Police officers including one who
OL,19,Fhad gone to the Netherlands and China
OL,20,Fto secure key evidence from drone data
OL,21,Frecords.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G16/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FIn July last year, the chief inspector
OL,8,Fof prisons Charlie Taylor warned of
OL,9,Fthe increased risk drones would pose
OL,10,Ffor smuggling drugs into prisons.
OL,12,FThe watchdog chief said: "There is a
OL,13,Flevel of risk that's posed by drones
OL,14,Fthat I think is different from what
OL,15,Fwe've seen in the past, and both with
OL,16,Fstuff coming in and ultimately the
OL,17,Fpotential for something even more
OL,18,Fserious to happen.
OL,26,@tD@ZOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G17/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772543470
OL,3,C'Deliveroo for prisons' gang jailed
OL,4,Cover weapons and drugs smuggled by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,F"What I'd like to see is that the
OL,8,Fprison service really get a grip of
OL,9,Fthis issue and and we'd like to see
OL,10,Fthe Government, security services
OL,11,Fcoming together, using technology,
OL,12,Fusing intelligence, so that this risk
OL,13,Fdoesn't materialise."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@UO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G18/18
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
